147
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:29,010
Do what you do best.

148
00:10:29,487 --> 00:10:30,867
Worry about the rest later.

149
00:10:37,214 --> 00:10:38,332
Is my daughter okay?

150
00:10:38,698 --> 00:10:40,107
Yeah, yeah, she's fine.

151
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:41,966
