155
00:10:51,145 --> 00:10:53,044
<i>Okay, I can find a weak spot.</i>

156
00:10:53,334 --> 00:10:56,225
But know this, sergeant,
if you hurt my daughter,

157
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:59,401
